/>\n<br />\nCredit: studio incendo"},{"pid":"61d1918a1a85edc6185a28619e89031e0aee428a","tid":2136782,"uid":33868,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"或者就咁叫臨時醫院<br />\n呢座野完全無靠過中央幫手起，係DH同HA加埋外判一齊短時間起"},{"pid":"c93d6b194fac0f80d2affa569047d71cc3cf53be","tid":2136782,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"入咗去係咪要收DNA?"},{"pid":"60cb20a42e619bac23b34644ba775eac5103bfb3","tid":2136782,"uid":195,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"麥嘉晉 Raymond Mak <br />\n<br />\n1h &middot; <br />\n《自願帖：代人澄清》<br />\n這幾天在很多群組，都看到下面的照片。很多朋友馬上說，感謝國家隊支持香港建立「方艙醫院」，甚為高興。<br />\n但我想自發代表這個項目裏面的朋友澄清，這個亞博的臨時醫院，是「香港醫院管理局的同事，上上下下自己努力建立出來的」。<br />\n國家隊是來做檢測和協助之後的改裝，但沒有參與「建立」亞博臨時醫院，他們應該在建立的時候還沒到香港。<br />\n我知道醫管局有很多事情，都做得不似預期。但他們做得好的地方，就要鼓勵他們，更不要把他們的努力成果，錯誤地交給其他人。<br />\n#支持一切默默耕耘實事求是朋友<br />\n#請分享出去讓更多人知道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1882277518665989/posts/2945675345659529/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1882277518665989%2Fposts%2F2945675345659529%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=19d32642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1882277518665989/posts/2945675345659529/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"8681bbedba92ec9b988356260aec0573800c6300","tid":2136782,"uid":253608,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"臨時醫院就臨時醫院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a935209bdf7760f232fcfe18d482c5c8fae4fe","tid":2136782,"uid":24443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9736053a3b69d990359933500c1fc48f3469137d","tid":2136782,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2Zw4PT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.